name: The Moon CD
description:
Felili’s belief that music equals freedom shines through in every song. From Felili’s sensuous voice gliding over an optimistic keyboard and bass line on lead single “Hotel” to the more stripped down acoustic vibe of songs like “The Moon” and “How Hard I Try”, each track on The Moon holds a surprise for the listener.  The Moon will be released on February 16th, 2010. 

Track Listing: 
1. Hotel
2. Far Away
3. How Hard I Try
4. Butterscotch
5. Paradise
6. No Way To Know
7. I See 
8. A Little 
9. Maribelle
10. The Moon
